------------------------------------------------------------------------
r5150 | olivier.salaun | 2008-09-30 17:05:11 +0200 (mar 30 sep 2008) | 10 lignes
Chemins modifiés :
   M /trunk/mail_tt2/listmaster_notification.tt2
   M /trunk/mail_tt2/listowner_notification.tt2
   M /trunk/mail_tt2/moderate.tt2
