Prepare 4.0.a6 version with S/MIME changes proposed by C. Mock

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2017 | salaun | 2003-09-18 16:12:39 +0200 (jeu 18 sep 2003) | 2 lignes
Chemins modifiés :
